snippet.title: Checkmate Showdown | Teaser
snippet.description:
First teaser for Checkmate Showdown

Crush your opponents in the arena and on the board in this multiplayer competitive tactical fighting game that mixes the strategical elegance of Chess with the fast-paced execution of fighting games. The ultimate competition. Got what it takes?

Co Developed by BadRez Games and ManaVoid Entertainment

https://www.checkmateshowdown.com/
https://discord.gg/gpMrfByn5H
https://twitter.com/Checkm8Showdown
https://www.tiktok.com/@checkmateshowdown
